      <title>俄罗斯就扣押资产向 Euroclear 寻求 2300 亿美元损失赔偿</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/russias-central-bank-seeks-230-billion-damages-belgiums-euroclear-moscow-court-2025-12-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯央行已在莫斯科提起诉讼，要求 Euroclear 赔偿 2300 亿美元，这标志着克里姆林宫警告欧盟计划使用冻结的俄罗斯资产支持乌克兰的法律噩梦的第一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/russias-central-bank-seeks-230-billion-damages-belgiums-euroclear-moscow-court-2025-12-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Dec 2025 07:05:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
